Correspondence is a Mac Application for keeping track of your letters to others.

We want to use it as our main Application for this purpose very, very soon.
When we announce this you can expect that we migrate the data you entered with great care.

* You can start to use the application
* Fork it, improve it and tell us about it :)
* We would like to get feedback about what can be done to improve it

The Code is released under the MIT License.